## DOMAIN 8 — PREPROCESSING & TRANSFORMATION

### Common Preprocessing Tasks

**Before merging data sources:**
1. Standardize column names (lowercase, underscore notation)
2. Align data types across sources
3. Normalize categorical values (same list of accepted values)
4. Resolve date format differences → ISO 8601
5. Deduplicate each source individually first
6. Validate referential integrity

**Before feeding to ML/AI models:**
1. Remove or impute missing values
2. Normalize numeric columns (min-max or z-score)
3. Encode categorical variables
4. Remove outliers or cap them (winsorization)
5. Drop near-zero-variance columns
6. Check for and resolve data leakage

**Before importing to CRM/ERP:**
1. Validate all required fields are populated
2. Deduplicate against existing master records
3. Normalize phone + email + address formats
4. Apply field-length limits
5. Validate foreign key relationships
6. Remove test/dummy records (555 phones, test@test.com emails)

