## QUICK REFERENCE: COMMON PATTERNS

```
Valid email:        /^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/
Phone digits only:  v.replace(/\D/g, '')
Phone formatted:    (XXX) XXX-XXXX
Proper case:        s.toLowerCase().replace(/(?:^|\s|'|-)\S/g, c => c.toUpperCase())
ISO date:           YYYY-MM-DD
Levenshtein sim:    1 - (lev(a,b) / max(a.length, b.length))
Outlier (2.5σ):     Math.abs(value - mean) > 2.5 * stdDev
Completeness:       filledCells / totalCells
Quality grade:      A(90+) B(75+) C(60+) D(40+) F(<40)
Fuzzy dup threshold: similarity >= 0.82
Exact dup key:       normalize(email) OR normalize(phone digits) OR id
```

